Overview:

The sinister Milkman holds the city of Las Cruces in his nasty criminal grip, and it's up to legendary black belt neurosurgeon Dr. Karate, disgraced athlete Steroid Jackson, renegade derby girl Hella Fistgerald, the mysterious Beekeeper, and the rest of the Fist Puncher team to deliver a dose of old-school justice.

Clean up tweakers on a Nude Beach, crash a Nazi Birthday Party, race ostriches across a barren desert, and explore a haunted graveyard as the Fist Puncher vigilantes attempt to restore peace to the lawless streets.
